data.description: This beautiful home built in 2017 and has 3 Bedrooms, a Loft & 2.5 Baths; Highlights/Features include but not limited to: Open Floor Plan Layout; Raised Ceilings; Kitchen w/ Island, Walk-in Pantry & Appliances; Dining / Living Room Space; Large Great Room open to Breakfast Nook & Kitchen; HUGE Owner's Suite w/ large Closet & Private Owner's Bath w/ Double Bowl Vanity, Garden Tub & Separate Shower; 2 nice sized Secondary Bedrooms; Secondary Bath w/ Dbl vanity; Loft that's perfect for a secondary Living / Entertaining Space; Upstairs Laundry Room; 2 Car Garage with Bump Out; Nice Yard Space that backs up to neighborhood green space; Great location! Just minutes to I-70, I-465 & the Geist Area; Highly Desired Mt. Vernon Schools! See it today!
